item.title: Halloween BABES! | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano: Hey Babe! | EP 100
item.description:
THE BABES are flourishing in the Halloween spirit!!!! Throw on a costume and get DOWN WITH THE BABES!!! Shout out The Beatles and their awful name. Sal wants to start journaling to really get a hold of his life. Living in the moment is the key to being happy. The babes talk about some of their favorite places to travel. Ireland is a magical place. Chris talks about his love for rainbows and scones. Johnny Depp and his lawyer are dating!! Spicy latinas are life! Tragedy is a part of life. Chris is obsessed with the watcher on netflix. Is Richard Kind dead?!?!? Sal talks about his dinner club. Appreciate the small things itll add up to BIG THINGS. Poop is in all food always......have you ever spit in someones food? Chris breaks down his new diet and how hard it is to diet. Is coffee good or bad? Is cold water better or worse than warm water. Cold showers help your body but SUCK.
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!

What exactly is a Zaddy? Zaddy vs Dilf. Who do we think the hottest zaddies are? Clueless is a classic movie. Paul Rudd is the best! What is the most watched movie of all time. Subway has a crazy new promotion if you get a subway tattoo on your chest or back. Subway is OUT OF CONTROL! Chris goes to the beach and things go SOUTH. Chris connects with new friends on Staten Island. What's the worst job in nyc? Sal has a nightmare show on the road. Kid Cudi gets things thrown at him on stage at Rolling Loud music festival. Chris needs to get a new car! Chris meets Riff Raff......HEY BABE!

item.title: Flabbergasted AS F | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 86
item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! This week the babes are hella flabbergasted! Shout out Lizzo! What is the mystery behind being a twin. The babes wanna run away to a Christmas village and get lost in vibes. What's going on at the North Pole?! Sal remembers the time a person he knew wouldn't stop sneezing! What's worse than an itch you can't itch. The babes learn about a crazy twin story. Two twins lived the same life but didn't meet till late in life. What is a soul? What happens when one twin gets fat. Chris is an only child and it changed his life. Chris got rid of all his clothes and feels free. Sal is haunted by the clothes he has lost. Joe Gatto would just leave his clothes at Impractical Jokers live shows. Who has more unopened emails Chris vs Sal?!?! The babes read the first texts that were sent to their phone. HEY BABES!

item.title: Secret Impractical Jokers PUNISHMENT with Andrew Santino | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 84
item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! This week the babes are LIVE FROM JOEY ROSES!!! They are joined by comedian @Andrew Santino from @Bad Friends Shout out Hotels Tonight! Booking hotels day of is freedom. Sal has a nightmare experience at a hotel on the road. Chris loves going on impulsive trips with no plans. Pack a book bag and GO BABES! Is over planning a bad thing? Sal talks a bout a brutal punishment they can never get on air for Impractical Jokers. Shout out Megabus! Are you pro or anti vestibule? Benjamin Franklin woulda got MURKED on Shark Tank. Clean versions of music on radio STINK. A man saves his own father after a heart attack. Chris got pulled over for driving crazy. Andrew talks about his friendship with Patrick Mahomes II. Andrew has been going on adventures around the world! Peaches used to mean something else. Prostate exams are LIT FAM. Bobby Lee walked out of the new Jurassic Park movie. Top Guns secret message. HEY BABE!

item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! This week the babes are LIVE FROM JOEY ROSES!!! They are joined by comedians Ari Shaffir & Joe DeRosa. Chrissy goes full philosophy all over everyones asses. Would you want a person chef or driver?! Sal never has to pee. What height makes you a "lil person". How tall is Danny DeVito? Awkward stories from the bedroom. DeRosa has pulled out his back and is PAIN. Ari talks about filming his special "Jew". Chris is a flake. The worst tattoos. Sal talks about one of his classmates who said the craziest thing in front of the class. Joe wants him and Chris to get the tattoos they promised the fans. Ari's dog joins the program and does a crying trick. Who is playing the new Mr.Smith in the new Mr and Mrs Smith tv series. DeRosa goes OFF THE RAILS!

item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! This week the babes are indulging in some government conspiracies. The yellow brick road found on the bottom of the Pacific ocean. Shout out Graham Hancock!!! What is Göbekli Tepe and how does it impact history? In the 5th grade Sal attacked religion in front of the whole class. Youtube is an addiction. Ancient forest found in sink hole in China. A dead eye ball is brought back to life. Would you opt out of death if possible? Would you wanna outlive everybody? What is the Mandela effect? How will we be remembered in the future? Chris teaches Sal about MK-Ultra. Lost civilizations have peaked Chris' interest! How do full societies go missing? Imagine 5,000 years in the future......Chris goes in on some youtube rabbit holes. Don't let people ruin your day. Was Noah's Ark a hoax?!? Chris has an amazing Fat Joe story. Crazy fight happens in front of the Comedy Cellar.

item.title: Guido Magician with Mark Normand | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 65
item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! The babes are joined by comedian Mark Normand!!! The guys are welcomed by Mark Normand who you know from his special Out To Lunch and appearances on Comedy Central and Netflix. Guys get straight into and are shocked that Chet Hanks claims he wasn't raised by a good male role model. HIS DAD IS TOM HANKS! Do you think Tom Hanks is a good role model? I mean that Jamaican accent says a lot.. The three quickly transition into another topic to where we learn, Bill Hader stole a ravioli bit from Chris!
Do you know what a Hermès Birkin bag is? Or how much it costs?? For a Berkin bag Mark will be sure to sing whatever you want. Julia Fox was lucky enough to celebrate her birthday with Kanye West who gave all her friends Birkin Bags. Those babies go up to 400,000 dollars! WILD!
We learn that the boys enjoy a good drink, but don't do drugs, BUT enjoy edibles. Headlines are read and it makes the 3 question, Are we going to sh*t?! Is this armageddon? Hollywood signs everyone, even the Tinder Swindler!
Mark is getting married in New Orleans. Shane Gillis, Dan Soder, Tim Dillon will be there and so will Yamineka! Will his wedding turn into a comedy show?! Mark tells us about growing up in New Orleans and getting two weeks off from school for Mardi Gras. Sal shares a story about being on a float in Mardi Gras with Harry Connick Jr. !!!!
Chris tells us about Harpers Ferry in West Virginia and that we have to go! From there we get a History lesson from Chrissy histories about colonial times. Soon after, we learn that Victoria Secret hired a model with down syndrome for the first time. That brings the conversation to talking about Miss America Show Us Your Shoes Parade, home break ins and is avocado a dessert? Rate us on iTunes! https://linktr.ee/Nopreshnetwork Follow The Show! Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/heybabepod/ Twitter - https://twitter.com/heybabepod

item.title: The Nightingale Pledge | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 34
item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
The babes are back and jump right into a few crazy stories from Chrissy D's physical therapy days. What was inside of one of his strangest patients?! We find out that Chris took The Nightingale Pledge when he started his career in physical therapy. Strange things happen when you work in physical therapy. Why are doctors always drunk? Shout out healthcare workers! One of Chrissy Chaos' friends walked in on his wife cheating on him with a famous baseball player. Sal had something awful happen at a party with Derek Jeter. A new species of humans was found in China. Shout out root beer floats! Cake mix market is a hustle. How much money would it take for you to eat a fried Tarantula? What do Tarantulas taste like? We find out that Chris' girlfriend used to own a alligator...WHAT?! Why do people own weird exotic pets?! HEY BABE!

item.title: The Richest Person in History | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 32
item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES! The babes are back and are talking richest people in history! The episode starts with Chris telling the story of how he BOMBED his stand up comedy set for the Met's owner Steve Cohen's birthday. Chris can't say Impossible. Do any words have in instead of im? How much money would you need to never work ever again? Who was the richest person to ever live on Earth? How many billionaires are on Earth right now? Cristiano Ronaldo Causes Coca-Cola's Value to Plummet $4 Billion. What's going on with Steven Seagal? Steven Seagal has left the US and became a big part of Russia. Steven Seagal is close friends with Vladimir Putin?! Chris has seen Sal get mad before. You ever realize that at one point in your life you were better at basketball than Lebron? Sal went on a tour of Australia. Wedding horror stories! Why is common law married a thing? Is broad bad to call a woman? Can you call your girlfriend the old bag? SHOUT OUT TOM BRADY!!!! Rate us on iTunes! https://linktr.ee/Nopreshnetwork Follow The Show! item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This episode the Babes talk their fav products YASSS! Their favorite grocery stores. Sal admits if he was to marry a store it would be a Wegmans. Chris talk's about the first time his mother let him to go the store alone and things took a turn for the tragic. Sal's dad went to an A&P during the holidays and some guy lost his mind and attacked Sal's father! Chris talks about a wild story he read in the news. A 70 year old ex marine is on a bus of seniors when 2 robbers stop the bus with guns....the 70 year old man kills the 20 year old robbers.....WHAT! Are there old tall people alive?! Chris' daughter interrupts the show YASSSSSSS. Shout out Trader Joes! Chris gets smashed off strawberry margaritas and has a hang over BAD. Olives make Chris sick. What's the deal with mayo *Seinfeld voice* Octopuses are sus what's up with them? Are they aliens? The babes talk calamari and how they know nothing about the ocean. What's the smartest creature on the planet? Filmmakers are wild like how did abraham lincoln vampire slayer get made? Chris talks about what happens when you turn 100. Chris talks about how him and Sal are just different men than their grandfathers. Sal talks about his uncle with a dent in his head who's a REAL man. Chris and Sal get scared of haunted house. The babes share their experiences with ghosts. HEY BABE!

Make your friends think you're skipping the check and run out of the restaurant but secretly pay the bill. Jesus was paleo right? What did people eat back then. Chris talks about the time he was served pasta at a wedding and it had cigarette ash in it. Sal talks about the time he witnessed a guest order a pizza to a wedding. Ever call someone by the wrong name? Shout out Dave Attell he's a legend! Who would win in a fight Ronald McDonald or the King from Burger King? Sal and Chris finally kiss.

item.description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This episode the Babes talk Sal hurt his neck, Chris is really into Homeland, Sex crimes at Rockefeller Center during Christmas are INSANE, are underwear called unmentionables?, spy cameras are getting too good, Shoutout to KFC for doing our bit, Sal gets into some road rage and beats up a guys car, Chris’ old boss has weird road rage and things get shitty, Chris’ GF told him that she would us poop senders as revenge if he screws up, Ends up poop senders is an amazing service and hopefully a new sponsor!, Who do you think we are sending poop to?, Homeland shows a vag wiping scene and it haunts Chris’ memory, subtitles or no subtitles?, 6 Pence None the Richer music talk, we talk culture club and how to make music, Chris breaks down what dancing does to the human brain, the guys will perform an original song at the first live show, theres only 1 song that will make Chris cry, theres 8 songs that will make Sal cry, shout out whitney houston YAS!, Chris refuses to wait on line but Sal doesnt mind a line, Sal goes to an Elton John concert and rumor is Sir Elton was pissing his pants the whole concert, if you could have one person singing voice who would it be? Chris goes Whitney Houston or Adele, Sal Aretha Franklin, who would you trade places with in history?, Sal asks Chris if he knows a song….
